#  Nmap Port Scan Detection

## Objective

Detect reconnaissance activity using SYN scan patterns.

## Steps

1. Run scan:
   nmap -sS <target_ip>
2. Capture traffic in Wireshark

## Filter

tcp.flags.syn == 1 and tcp.flags.ack == 0

## Findings

* Multiple SYN packets
* No completed handshake

## Conclusion

Indicates stealth port scanning activity.
